  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>You create a 10-foot-radius, 20-foot-tall &amp;Reference[cylinder]{cylinder} of magical energy centered on a point on the ground that you can see within range. Glowing runes appear wherever the &amp;Reference[cylinder]{cylinder} intersects with the floor or other surface.</p>\n<p>Choose one or more of the following types of creatures: celestials, elementals, &amp;Reference[fey]{fey}, fiends, or &amp;Reference[undead]{undead}. The circle affects a creature of the chosen type in the following ways:</p>\n<p>The creature can’t willingly enter the &amp;Reference[cylinder]{cylinder} by nonmagical means. If the creature tries to use teleportation or interplanar travel to do so, it must first succeed on a &amp;Reference[cha]{Charisma} saving throw.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The creature has disadvantage on attack rolls against targets within the &amp;Reference[cylinder]{cylinder}.</li>\n<li>Targets within the &amp;Reference[cylinder]{cylinder} can’t be &amp;Reference[charmed]{charmed}, &amp;Reference[frightened]{frightened}, or possessed by the creature.</li>\n<li>When you cast this spell, you can elect to cause its magic to operate in the reverse direction, preventing a creature of the specified type from leaving the &amp;Reference[cylinder]{cylinder} and protecting targets outside it.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></em> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the duration increases by 1 hour for each slot level above 3rd.</p>\n</div>",
      "chat": ""
    },
